# Repository-wide text normalization (see gitattributes(5), GitHub "Configuring Git to handle line endings").
# All detected text files use LF in the object database and in the working tree, independent of local
# core.autocrlf defaults, without per-file workarounds.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary and non-text overrides (keep Git's text heuristic away from byte-accurate payloads).
*.7z binary
*.a binary
*.bmp binary
*.bz2 binary
*.cso binary
*.dds binary
*.dll binary
*.dylib binary
*.exe binary
